headline: Trane Technologies Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, June 05, 2025--The Board of Directors of Trane Technologies plc (NYSE:TT), a global climate innovator, declared a quarterly dividend of $0.94 per ordinary share, or $3.76 per share annualized. The dividend is payable on September 30, 2025, to shareholders of record as of September 5, 2025.
